cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper deals with the problem of translating videos to natural language, which involves both computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep neural networks for language generation, which falls under the category of cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses language generation metrics and human evaluation, which are related to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with video data, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia).
